<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Password Reset | Sarahah</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .envelope {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10bbb3 0%, #0a8a84 100%);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }

    .app-name {
      color: white;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-top: 7px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #10bbb3;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .otp-container {
      margin: 40px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .otp-code {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10bbb3 0%, #0a8a84 100%);
      color: white;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 187, 179, 0.3);
    }

    .note {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #10bbb3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #10bbb3;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #0a8a84;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(16, 187, 179, 0.4);
    }

    .expiry-notice {
      color: #dc3545;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 28px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="envelope">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dxyhgxd3j/image/upload/v1753913646/logo300_oaewnk.png" alt="Sarahah Logo" class="logo" />
          <div class="app-name">Sarahah</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        <p>We received a request to reset your Sarahah account password. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your identity:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-container">
          <div class="otp-code"><%= OTP %></div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="expiry-notice">This OTP will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
        
        <div class="note">
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>For security reasons, please don't share this OTP with anyone. Our team will never ask you for your password or OTP.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you,<br>The Sarahah Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Sarahah App. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to you as part of your Sarahah account security.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>